---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout title="Case Study: How Dragon Spirit Martial Arts Achieved 68% Trial Conversion | Lead Flow North">
  <article class="py-12 md:py-20">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <!-- Back Link -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-8">
        <a href="/industries/fitness-gyms/martial-arts" class="inline-flex items-center text-sky-600 hover:text-sky-700 dark:text-sky-300 font-medium">
          <svg class="w-4 h-4 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M15 19l-7-7 7-7"></path></svg>
          Back to Martial Arts
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <header class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center mb-12">
        <div class="flex items-center justify-center gap-4 mb-6">
          <span class="bg-green-100 text-green-700 px-3 py-1 rounded-full text-sm font-medium">Case Study</span>
          <span class="text-slate-500 dark:text-slate-400 text-sm">5 min read</span>
        </div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-6">
          How Dragon Spirit Martial Arts Achieved 68% Trial Conversion
        </h1>
        <p class="text-xl text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 mb-8">
          A Halifax martial arts school transformed their student retention with marketing automation.
        </p>
      </header>

      <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto mb-12">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-red-600 rounded-2xl p-8 md:p-12 text-white">
          <div class="grid grid-cols-2 md:grid-cols-4 gap-8">
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">68%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Trial Conversion</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">2.4yrs</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Avg Membership</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">89%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Test Attendance</div>
            </div>
            <div class="text-center">
              <div class="text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold mb-2">52%</div>
              <div class="text-amber-100">Family Add-ons</div>
            </div>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <div class="prose prose-lg prose-slate dark:prose-invert max-w-none">

          <div class="bg-slate-100 p-6 rounded-xl my-8 not-prose">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mb-4">Client Overview</h3>
            <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-4 text-sm">
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Business:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Dragon Spirit Martial Arts</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Location:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Halifax, NS</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Type:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Martial arts school</span>
              </div>
              <div>
                <span class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300">Programs:</span>
                <span class="font-medium text-slate-900 dark:text-white ml-2">Taekwondo, kids & adults</span>
              </div>
            </div>
          </div>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Challenge</h2>

          <p>
            Master David Lee's school had excellent instructors but struggled with growth. Trial families didn't enroll. Students quit after yellow or orange belt. Only one child per family trained. Summer caused major churn.
          </p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Solution</h2>

          <p>We implemented trial follow-up sequences, belt test reminder automation, family expansion campaigns, parent progress updates, and summer retention programs with special camps.</p>

          <h2 class="text-2xl font-bold text-slate-900 dark:text-white mt-12 mb-4">The Results</h2>

          <p>Trial-to-membership conversion hit 68%. Average membership length extended to 2.4 years. Belt test attendance reached 89%. Family add-ons are at 52%. More students are achieving black belt than ever before.</p>

          <blockquote class="border-l-4 border-amber-500 pl-6 my-8">
            <p class="text-xl text-slate-700 dark:text-slate-300 italic mb-4">
              "The parent updates made the biggest difference. When parents see their child's progress and understand the character development happening, they commit long-term. Our retention transformed."
            </p>
            <cite class="text-slate-600 dark:text-slate-300 not-italic">â€” Master David Lee, Owner</cite>
          </blockquote>

          <div class="bg-gradient-to-r from-amber-600 to-red-600 p-8 rounded-xl text-white my-12">
            <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold mb-4 text-white">Ready to Grow Your School?</h3>
            <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center bg-white text-amber-600 px-6 py-3 rounded-lg font-semibold hover:bg-slate-100 transition">
              Book Your Free Demo
            </a>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </article>
</Layout>
